messages.content: Don't make assumptions about what values to plug into functions. Ask for clarification if a user request is ambiguous.

I don’t currently have access to your location. If you’d like, you can enable location services or provide your coordinates, and I can help you determine your city. Would you like to enable location services or share your latitude and longitude?
Sure, you can use location services.

Location services are already enabled. Please provide your latitude and longitude, or let me know if there is another way you’d like me to help determine your city. If your device can share your coordinates, please do so, and I’ll look up your location!
Sorry, I don't have that info. Could you try finding it with the location service?

I don’t have direct access to your device’s location; I rely on you to provide coordinates or location details. If your device or browser allows you to copy your location (latitude and longitude), you can share it here, and I’ll identify your city.

Unfortunately, without your coordinates or town name, I can’t determine your exact location. If you find a way to get your coordinates, just let me know!
Got it, I'll check on my phone and try to find it there.

That sounds great! Once you have your latitude and longitude from your phone, just let me know, and I’ll help identify your city. If you need guidance on how to find your coordinates, just ask—I’m happy to help!
You’re welcome! Take your time. Whenever you have your coordinates, just send them here and I’ll help you find your city. If you have any other questions or need assistance, feel free to ask!
